OL,5,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's been a fiery week, and every
OL,7,     Flast one of the B&Bers is unhappy
OL,8,     Fwith their feedback. So expect
OL,9,     Fmore fireworks when they meet up
OL,10,     Fonce again to find out who's won.
OL,11,G2100 24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     FThis episode focuses on some of
OL,13,     Fthe elderly patients who are
OL,14,     Ftreated at King's College
OL,15,     FHospital, including 83-year-old
OL,16,     FWilliam, who hasn't seen a doctor
OL,17,     Ffor 40 years.
